longBusinessSummary: Petro River Oil Corp., an independent energy company, focuses on the exploration and development of conventional oil and gas assets. It primarily holds interests in the Mid-Continent Region in Oklahoma, including Osage County and Kay County, Oklahoma. The company is based in New York, New York.
